{"DamageImmunities":[],"ConditionImmunities":[],"DamageResistances":[],"DamageVulnerability":[],"SavingThrowBonuses":["Wis +5","Cha +10"],"SkillBonuses":["Skill: Athletics (Str) +4 | (Str -1, Prof. 5, Bonus 0)","Skill: Perception (Wis) +6 | (Wis 1, Prof. 5, Bonus 0)","Skill: Deception (Cha) +10 | (Cha 5, Prof. 5, Bonus 0)","Skill: Intimidation (Cha) +10 | (Cha 5, Prof. 5, Bonus 0)"],"_Senses":[],"_Languages":[],"_Abilities":[{"Title":"Shapechanger","Description":"If the Luciaria Avisen isn't in sunlight or running water, it can use its action to polymorph into a Tiny bat or Medium cloud of mist, or back to its true form.\r\nWhile in bat form, the Luciaria Avisen can't speak, its walking speed is 5 feet, and it has a flying speed of 30 feet. Its statistics, other than its size and speed, are unchanged. Anything it is wearing transforms with it, but nothing it is carrying does. It reverts to its true form if it dies.\r\nWhile in mist form, the Luciaria Avisen can't take any actions, speak, or manipulate objects. It is weightless, has a flying speed of 20 feet, can hover and can enter a hostile creature's space and stop there. In addition if air can pass through a space, the mist can do so without squeezing, and it can't pass through water. It has advantage on Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution saving throws, and it is immune to all nonmagical damage, except the damage it takes from sunlight.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Legendary Resistance (3/Day)","Description":"If the Luciaria Avisen fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Misty Escape","Description":"When it drops to 0 hit points outside its resting place, the Luciaria Avisen transofrms into a cloud of mist (as in the Shapechanger trait) instead of falling unconscious, provided that it isn't in sunlight or running water. If it can't transform, it is destroyed.\r\nWhile it has 0 hit points in mist form, it can't revert to its Luciaria Avisen form, and it must reach its resting place within 2 hours or be destroyed. Once in its resting place, it reverts to its Luciaria Avisen form. It is then paralyzed until it regains at least 1 hit point. After spending 1 hour in its resting place with 0 hit points, it regains 1 hit point.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Regeneration","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen regains 20 hit points at the start of its turn if it has at least 1 hit point and isn't in sunlight or running water. If the Luciaria Avisen takes radiant damage or damage from holy water, this trait doesn't function at the start of the Luciaria Avisen's next turn.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Spider Climb","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen can climb difficult surfaces, including upside down on ceilings, without needing to make an ability check.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Vampire Weaknesses","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen has the following flaws:\r\n<i>Forbiddance.</i> The Luciaria Avisen can't enter a residence without an invitation from one of the occupants.\r\n<i>Harmed by Running Water.</i> The Luciaria Avisen takes 20 acid damage if it ends its turn in running water.\r\n<i>Stake to the Heart.</i> If a piercing weapon made of wood is driven into the Luciaria Avisen's heart while the Luciaria Avisen is incapacitated in its resting place, the Luciaria Avisen is paralyzed until the stake is removed.\r\n<i>Sunlight Hypersensitivity.</i> The Luciaria Avisen takes 20 radiant damage when it starts its turn in sunlight. While in sunlight, it has disadvantage on attack rolls and ability checks.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Lucky (3/day)","Description":"Luciaria can roll a D20 and choose which roll to use for any D20 roll ","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Robe of the Archmagi","Description":"Luciaria has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"warlock Spellcasting","Description":"warlock|Charisma|15|NotInnate|1,1,1,1,3,0,0,0,0|0:Eldritch Blast,0:Friends,0:Mage Hand,0:Minor Illusion,0:Sacred Flame,0:Thaumaturgy,0:Vicious Mockery,1:Charm Person,1:Command,1:Hellish Rebuke,2:Invisibility,2:Misty Step,3:Clairvoyance,3:Fly,4:Evard's Black Tentacles,5:Dream,5:Flame Strike,5:Hallow,5:Telekinesis,|","isDamage":false,"isSpell":true,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Actions":[{"Title":"Multiattack (Vampire Form Only)","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen makes two attacks, only one of which can be a bite attack.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Unarmed Strike (Vampire Form Only)","Description":"","isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Weapon Attack","Bonus":"9","Reach":5,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one creature","HitDiceNumber":1,"HitDiceSize":8,"HitDamageBonus":4,"HitAverageDamage":8,"HitText":"Instead of dealing damage, the Luciaria Avisen can grapple the target (escape DC 18).","HitDamageType":"bludgeoning"},"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Bite (Bat or Vampire Form Only)","Description":"","isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Weapon Attack","Bonus":"9","Reach":5,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one willing creature, or a creature that is grappled by the Luciaria Avisen, incapacitated or restrained.","HitDiceNumber":1,"HitDiceSize":6,"HitDamageBonus":4,"HitAverageDamage":7,"HitText":"plus 10 (3d6) necrotic damage. The target's hit point maximum is reduced by an amount equal to the necrotic damage taken, and the Luciaria Avisen regains hit points equal to that amount. The reduction lasts until the target finishes a long rest. The target dies if this effect reduces its hit point maximum to 0. A humanoid slain in this way and then buried in the ground rises the following night as a Luciaria Avisen spawn under the Luciaria Avisen's control.","HitDamageType":"piercing"},"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Charm","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen targets one humanoid it can see within 30 feet of it. If the target can see the Luciaria Avisen, the target must succeed on a DC 17 Wisdom saving throw against this magic or be charmed by the Luciaria Avisen. The charmed target regards the Luciaria Avisen as a trusted friend to be heeded and protected. Although the target isn't under the Luciaria Avisen's control, it takes the Luciaria Avisen's requests or actions in the most favourable way it can, and is a willing target for the Luciaria Avisen's bite attack.\r\nEach time the Luciaria Avisen or the Luciaria Avisen's companions do anything harmful to the target, it can repeat the saving throw, ending the effect on itself on a success. Otherwise, the effect lasts 24 hours or until the Luciaria Avisen is destroyed, is on a different plane of existence than the target, or takes a bonus action to end the effect.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Children of the Night (1/Day)","Description":"The Luciaria Avisen magically calls 2d4 swarms of bats or rats, provided that the sun isn't up. While outdoors, the Luciaria Avisen can call 3d6 wolves instead. The called creatures arrive in 1d4 rounds, acting as allies of the Luciaria Avisen and obeying its spoken commands. The beasts remain for 1 hour, until the Luciaria Avisen dies, or until the Luciaria Avisen dismisses them as a bonus action.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[{"Traits":[{"Title":"Move","Ability":"The Luciaria Avisen moves up to its speed without provoking opportunity attacks."},{"Title":"Unarmed Strike","Ability":"The Luciaria Avisen makes one unarmed strike."},{"Title":"Bite (Costs 2 Actions)","Ability":"The Luciaria Avisen makes one bite attack."}],"Title":"Vampire Legendary Actions"}],"_advancedSpells":[],"_advancedSpellData":[],"Title":"","STR":8,"DEX":12,"CON":17,"INT":12,"WIS":15,"CHA":22,"proficency":5,"Speed":"30 ft.","AC":"17","HP":"120 (16d8 + 48)","CR":{"Index":19,"CR":"16","profBonus":5,"ArmorClass":18,"AttackBonus":9,"SaveDC":18,"LowHP":296,"HighHP":310,"XP":15000},"CreatureName":"Luciaria Avisen","CreatureSize":"Medium","CreatureType":"Undead (Human Vampire)","CreatureAlign":"Chaotic Evil","unique":false,"CreatureGender":"Female","LegendaryActions":"3"}